  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Benefit: A silent spell can be cast with no verbal components. Spells without verbal components are not affected. A silent spell uses up a spell slot one level higher than the spell's actual level.\nSpecial: Bard spells cannot be enhanced by this metamagic feat.",
